msgid "Seyyathāpi te, bhikkhave, dutiyā migajātā tathūpame ahaṃ ime dutiye samaṇabrāhmaṇe vadāmi. "
msgstr "This second group of ascetics and brahmins is just like the second herd of deer, I say. "

