msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn25:10.19"
msgid "Te tattha ananupakhajja amucchitā bhojanāni bhuñjamānā na madaṃ āpajjiṃsu, amattā samānā na pamādaṃ āpajjiṃsu, appamattā samānā na yathākāmakaraṇīyā ahesuṃ mārassa amusmiṃ nivāpe amusmiñca lokāmise. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn25:10.20"
msgid "Api ca kho evaṃdiṭṭhikā ahesuṃ—"
msgstr "Still, they had such views as these: "

msgctxt "mn25:10.21"
msgid "sassato loko itipi, asassato loko itipi; "
msgstr "‘The world is eternal’ or ‘The world is not eternal’; "

msgctxt "mn25:10.22"
msgid "antavā loko itipi, anantavā loko itipi; "
msgstr "‘The world is finite’ or ‘The world is infinite’; "

msgctxt "mn25:10.23"
msgid "taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīraṃ itipi, aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīraṃ itipi; "
msgstr "‘The soul and the body are the same thing’ or ‘The soul and the body are different things’; "

msgctxt "mn25:10.24"
msgid "hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā itipi, na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā itipi, hoti ca na ca hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā itipi, neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā itipi. "
msgstr "or that after death, a Realized One exists, or doesn’t exist, or both exists and doesn’t exist, or neither exists nor doesn’t exist. "

